      <title>斯洛伐克总理预计枪击事件发生数周后将重返工作岗位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-05/slovak-premier-expects-to-return-to-work-in-weeks-after-shooting</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在5月15日的暗杀事件中受伤的斯洛伐克总理罗伯特·菲佐表示，他希望在本月底或7月份重返工作岗位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-05/slovak-premier-expects-to-return-to-work-in-weeks-after-shooting</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 15:55:57 GMT</pubDate>
