      <title>普京旗舰论坛为精英子女提供舞台</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-05/putin-s-flagship-forum-offers-stage-to-children-of-russian-elite</link>
      <description><![CDATA[本周，弗拉基米尔·普京将他的家乡圣彼得堡变成了权力中心，举办了一场重要的经济活动。在俄罗斯前帝国首都举行的这次会议正日益成为克里姆林宫精英子女们的世代展示。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-05/putin-s-flagship-forum-offers-stage-to-children-of-russian-elite</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>唐纳德·特朗普请求法官解除封口费案的禁言令</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-04/donald-trump-asks-ny-judge-to-lift-gag-order-in-hush-money-case</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普要求主审其封口费审判的纽约法官解除对此案的禁言令，称在陪审团上周判定他犯有 34 项重罪后，限制前总统言论的基础“已不复存在”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-04/donald-trump-asks-ny-judge-to-lift-gag-order-in-hush-money-case</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Jun 2024 23:02:22 GMT</pubDate>
